{"tid":902629,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴呢啲櫈坐到腰酸頸痛","createTime":"2018-11-15T03:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T09:46:31.000Z","uid":209157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27d7566f5813e183e0d03eeb4f0e3d78e7368ad6","tid":902629,"uid":209157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H9xgHOh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH9xgHOh.jpg&h=7353fee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVpKRHo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVpKRHo.png&h=c3c96f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有乜理由將個尖尖位頂住個頭架 仲要成個身向前靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住以前九巴白板車嗰啲櫈 比較軟 個頭枕都好舒服 而家啲車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差咁啲啦<br />\n<br />\n&quot;香港執業脊醫協會創會主席陳允灝建議，乘客可盡量「坐到最入」，身體要貼近椅背，「用上半身嘅力挨落張櫈，畀張櫈承受體重。」他又指，汽車座位上，頭枕的功能性大於舒適，一旦發生意外，可防止頭部過度向後拗，因此即使「枕唔到」，都並非太大問題。 此外，他建議巴士乘客在許可情況下「揀位坐」，「椅背最理想係傾斜110度，巴士最後嗰排角度較直，有腰痛人士應該避免。」&quot;<br />\n<br />\n啲櫈本身設計唔舒服 幾聽醫生話都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fbab5f840211e4917be07c15cf128ce18f04b1","tid":902629,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"設計比矮人坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f94e6cbbde2980bdaaaa3de889c56dcbd3adae6","tid":902629,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"月經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523dc48bf38aed44c058b257103d6d734af3a112","tid":902629,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"設計係要你地保持清醒"},{"pid":"d0d8dc17e55974be7adbd9bec8391f5c9c60093f","tid":902629,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37